Acceptance tests:

Behat/bin/behat  -p phantomjs --tags @wip -c Behat/behat.yml    # will run the scenarios tagged as @wip
Behat/bin/behat  -p phantomjs --tags ~@wip -c Behat/behat.yml    # will run all the scenarios but those tagged as @wip
Behat/bin/behat  -p phantomjs  -c Behat/behat.yml    # will run all the scenarios

Functional tests:

* How to install:

On Mac, using homebrew:

brew install phantomjs
brew install casperjs


(Alternatively, both can be installed with npm)

* To run all the tests:

casperjs test tests/*.js
